data.description: A Great Investment Opportunity!  A lovely 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 1/2 duplex. With almost 1,200 square feet, has tons of living space along with a one car garage and a nice sized lot.  This Solid Concrete Block HALF DUPLEX On a quiet street in Cocoa has lots of charm, and plenty of outdoor space for kids to play!  The kitchen has all wood cabinets, is open to dining/living, tile throughout with carpet in bedrooms! EASY ACCESS TO 520, I-95, SHOPPING, RESTAURANTS, ORLANDO INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT, THEME PARKS, KSC, THE PORT AND THE BEACH!
